snippet.title: The Path To Die: Pre-Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
The Path To Die is an adventure and action videogame based in the feudal Japan, where you play as a samurai fighting against your enemies in a huge imperial palace. 

Your gamepad is your sword, use it! 

Coming soon on Kickstarter.

-----------------------
